Renart Jewelry - Product Listing Application
Full-stack jewelry e-commerce application with real-time gold pricing.
Live Demo

Application: https://renart-jewelry.vercel.app
Backend API: https://renart-jewelry-production.up.railway.app

Features

RESTful API with dynamic pricing formula
Real-time gold price integration
Responsive carousel with touch/swipe support
Color picker (Yellow, White, Rose Gold)
5-star rating system
Price and popularity filtering
Mobile responsive design

Tech Stack

Backend: Node.js, Express.js, Railway
Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS, Vercel
API: metals.live for gold pricing

Installation
bash# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/baskann/renart-jewelry.git

# Backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
API Endpoints

GET /api/products - List products
GET /api/health - Health check


